95
00:09:49,640 --> 00:09:52,320
Look, on the table behind you,
there's a utility bill.

96
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:55,006
It says 23 Kingsbury Green on it.
Look at it.

97
00:09:55,400 --> 00:09:57,004
